OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784591296
OL,3,CUkraine launches huge drone attack on
OL,4,CMoscow following Russian strikes
OL,6,FUkraine launched a 400-drone attack on
OL,7,FMoscow in the early hours of Monday
OL,8,Fmorning, Russian officials said.
OL,10,FSergey Sobyanin, the Mayor of Moscow,
OL,11,Fsaid on Telegram that the drones
OL,12,Fstruck the capital between 8.30pm on
OL,13,FSunday and 5am Monday local time, and
OL,14,Fthat Russian air defence forces had
OL,15,Fintercepted most.
OL,17,FHe said some people had been injured
OL,18,Fin the strikes. No deaths have been
OL,19,Freported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
