OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784591296
OL,3,CUkraine launches huge drone attack on
OL,4,CMoscow following Russian strikes
OL,6,FSmoke was seen billowing in the
OL,7,FPodolsk region, south of the city
OL,8,Fcentre, and emergency services
OL,9,Fattended the areas of destruction.
OL,11,FUkraine's President Volodymyr
OL,12,FZelenskyy confirmed the strikes and
OL,13,Fsaid his forces also hit two tankers
OL,14,Fand four cargo ships in the Black Sea.
OL,16,FIt comes after a bombardment of
OL,17,FRussian strikes hit Ukraine on Sunday,
OL,18,Fin what Zelenskyy called the "largest
OL,19,FRussian ballistic missile attacks to
OL,20,Fdate".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
