CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784591296
OL,3,CUkraine launches huge drone attack on
OL,4,CMoscow following Russian strikes
OL,6,FIn Kyiv, one person was killed and 15
OL,7,Fothers injured in Russian missile and
OL,8,Fdrone attacks, Ukraine's State
OL,9,FEmergency Service said. Thirteen
OL,10,Fpeople were injured, including two
OL,11,Fchildren, in strikes in a rural area
OL,12,Fin Zaporizhzhia, Ukraine.
OL,14,FUkraine has also been targeting
OL,15,FRussia's oil and logistics facilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
