OL,3,CUkraine launches huge drone attack on
OL,4,CMoscow following Russian strikes
OL,6,FOn Saturday, July 18, Russian
OL,7,Fofficials said that at least eight
OL,8,Fpeople had been killed and 62 injured
OL,9,Fafter Ukrainian drone strikes hit two
OL,10,Flogistics warehouses in the city of
OL,11,FTambov, Russia.
OL,13,FPosting on social media platform X,
OL,14,FZelenskyy said: "We are justly
OL,15,Fresponding to every Russian strike on
OL,16,Four cities and communities.
OL,18,F"This war must be ended, and that is
OL,19,Fpossible only by intensifying pressure
OL,20,Fon the sole cause of this war `
OL,21,FRussia."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
